    narr:generatedFrom "d1b09a828565de86" ;
    narr:narration """This hub gathers the corpus's metaphor and rhetorical-device observations, dominated by a single move: mapping technical domains onto narrative and cognition. The conceptual core is physics — narrative as [velocity/acceleration vector in particle systems](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_2), distilled to the [steering-vector frame](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_SteeringVector), with the [2012 bird-flocking origin story](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_2) and the recurring [worldview-as-installable-program](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_Metaphor_InstallableProgram) idiom. Infrastructure analogies recur: [Git for AI collaboration](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_GitMetaphor), the [GitHub category-creation pitch](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_GitHubMetaphor), and the customer's CTO's native [memory-as-code/PRs/unit-tests](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_EngineeringMetaphor). The [optometrist metaphor](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_OptometristMetaphor) serves as the product's sustained explanatory anchor (eye chart, refraction, lens). Other clusters: [archery/arrows](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_5), [brain personification](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_BrainPersonification), [Apple-vs-Microsoft simplicity](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_AppleComparison), physical-exertion business framing like [mountain-climbing base camp](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_Tranche1_MountainMetaphor), and business shorthand — [consulting as manufacturing](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_BusinessShape_2), [moat](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_Metaphor_Moat), [rainmakers](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_Metaphor_Rainmakers). Dates run 2025-05 through 2026-05.""" ;
